      • changeLevel

        void changeLevel(Log.LogEntryLevel level)
        Changes log level of this component. Thus it will log only logs with the same severity as given level, or bigger.
        Parameters:
        level - the severity level to be set to this log component
        See Also:
        Log.LogEntryLevel

      • clear

        Clears the all messages in log. Waits until log is cleared.
